description: The suspect had received orders from Syria and Iraq to carry out an attack, the government says.
title: Turkey detains top Islamic State commander in raid
title_page: Turkey detains top Islamic State commander in raid - BBC News
maintext: Ozden had been planning to carry out attacks with groups of 10 to 12 IS terrorists, Mr Soylu said. He referred to the suspect as the group's "emir" in Turkey.
